*<!here>  is today’s activity*

*grateful friday!*:innocent:

*in life, it is important to be thankful for even little good deeds that people have done to you or things that have happened to you. today we will focus on Joanne academy related deeds and community.*
• think of someone/some people within the Joanne academy community who have done good deed/s to you within the past  11 weeks (however big or small, action or words).
• write on slack about what they did and attach that *thank you poster* below to your message. if you have more than 1 person you are grateful to/for please use a comma (,) after the first person’s deed to add the second person and their deed. (*no limit to the number of people you can thank today*).
• use this format;
i am grateful to……….[_*tag person 1*_] for [_*mention person 1’s deed/s*_], [_*tag person 2*_] for [_*mention person 2’s deed/s] ……………….*_

*remember to attach the thank you poster below.*
